name: Breathe
description:
Where do you go to take time to breathe?
This photograph was taken in the Jebel Marrah Mountains in Darfur in 2008. I sat there that evening to recharge after my day and take in the beauty of my surroundings for some respite.
The conflict in Darfur is still ongoing at the time of minting.

Taking a moment to find tranquility to feel grounded and at peace is important no matter where we are or life's circumstances; for some this is a challenge to do. I hope this gives you a moment to breathe, feel calm and practice self love xxx.
